wait until (till) 等到某时候
We can't wait until Tuesday. We're having a party tonight. 我们不能等到星期二。我们今晚就要举办派对。
We'll just wait until Allan gets home. 我们要等到亚伦到家。
Let's just wait until I'm on leave. 我们就等到我放假吧。
I guess we have to wait until he comes back. 我猜我们得等到他回来了。
When do you think he'll get back? 你觉得他什么时候能回来？